description: Curbside Cupcakes is a mobile cupcake company serving Washington DC. Look for the pink cupcake truck Downtown and around Capitol Hill bringing cupcake bliss right to your door.We offer individual cupcakes for your immediate enjoyment and delivery for your next meeting, party, or event!Bringing cupcake bliss right to your door!Curbside Cupcakes is the newest member of DC's cupcake craze!  We are a mobile truck delivering gourmet cupcakes to your office, home, or event.  Look for us at a curb near you!To get an inside look at the minds behind this great truck, check out the Roaming Hunger blog here: http://roaminghunger.com/blog/4088/featured-food-truck-of-the-week-5
name: Curbside Cupcakes
